  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sharks and Minnows is an exploration-based survival horror game where players scavenge a haunted swim center and must complete ten laps to escape.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/27f0f783d3396848616391fc5fa46da9.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/27f0f783d3396848616391fc5fa46da9.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/27f0f783d3396848616391fc5fa46da9.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One autumn afternoon, your trip to the local pool takes a paranormal turn. After emerging from the water, you suddenly find yourself totally alone. Any attempt to leave just leads you back to the water.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/31f7048b98b11815451d085d5631fc7f.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/31f7048b98b11815451d085d5631fc7f.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/31f7048b98b11815451d085d5631fc7f.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you swim, the more your stamina drains, and running out has deadly consequences. The facility has scattered supplies that could replenish it, but you'll have to search for them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/a26fd66eb39ae75d351a3da350d22788.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/a26fd66eb39ae75d351a3da350d22788.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/a26fd66eb39ae75d351a3da350d22788.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's lonely. Will you ever make it home?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/f053e20df714090affa65a3cf2256179.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/f053e20df714090affa65a3cf2256179.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/f053e20df714090affa65a3cf2256179.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore deeper into the facility's alcoves for supplies, you get the sense that your search isn't solitary. If you aren't careful, you may end up trapped forever.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sharks and Minnows is an exploration-based survival horror game where players scavenge a haunted swim center and must complete ten laps to escape.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/27f0f783d3396848616391fc5fa46da9.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/27f0f783d3396848616391fc5fa46da9.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/27f0f783d3396848616391fc5fa46da9.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One autumn afternoon, your trip to the local pool takes a paranormal turn. After emerging from the water, you suddenly find yourself totally alone. Any attempt to leave just leads you back to the water.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/31f7048b98b11815451d085d5631fc7f.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/31f7048b98b11815451d085d5631fc7f.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/31f7048b98b11815451d085d5631fc7f.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you swim, the more your stamina drains, and running out has deadly consequences. The facility has scattered supplies that could replenish it, but you'll have to search for them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/a26fd66eb39ae75d351a3da350d22788.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/a26fd66eb39ae75d351a3da350d22788.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/a26fd66eb39ae75d351a3da350d22788.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's lonely. Will you ever make it home?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/f053e20df714090affa65a3cf2256179.poster.avif?t=1763433054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/f053e20df714090affa65a3cf2256179.webm?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446200/extras/f053e20df714090affa65a3cf2256179.mp4?t=1763433054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore deeper into the facility's alcoves for supplies, you get the sense that your search isn't solitary. If you aren't careful, you may end up trapped forever.</p>",
